            </span>
            <span class="absolute left-0 bottom-0 w-0 h-0.5 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#00B4D8] to-[#0077B6] transition-all duration-300 group-hover:w-full rounded-full shadow-[0_0_8px_rgba(0,180,216,0.6)]"></span>
          </a>
        </li>
